translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_f8a83119:
    # "Sarah stood outside on the balcony of her room. From here, the view stretched across the castle, the city and even far out to the fields beyond."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_593cb9fc:
    # "She had always loved this view, but now, it made her feel like ice ran through her chest."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_598d5e80:
    # "Several days had passed, and Varga's prediction had come true."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b5973c35:
    # "Hassar's army had moved fast, faster than anyone could have imagined, and they had arrived at the capital to finish a war that only just begun."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_58080313:
    # "Camped outside on the hills, Sarah saw an army larger than any she had ever seen in her life."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_287a41d7:
    # "Sarah's crossed her arms around her chest. She tried to exude a confidence she knew she didn't have."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_656ad785:
    # "They had prepared, but would it be enough?"
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_fb4fd44e:
    # "She didn't like the idea that her fate was now outside of her hands, and she was forced to wait like a lamb to the slaughter."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_4e3f0063:
    # "Sarah looked out over the battlefield below."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_c7367e71:
    # "Atop the hillside, Hassar's army had almost finished moblizing. Their front rank extended across the entire hillside, with every man sitting atop a horse."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_8da28c4a:
    # "Sarah had never seen anything like this."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_72092804:
    # "On their side, the walls were well fortified and rows of soldiers covered nearly every part of it."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_6d0ea4cd:
    # "The archers were in position, but without the signal to fire, had kept their bows loose."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_8af5043f:
    # "Out further in the field, Rosanna's army had taken to the center of the battlefield. Each regiment stood in perfect formation."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_f267aa9d:
    # "The flanks were covered by the heavy cavalry, most provided by Marion's family, Achillea. Their soldiers wore full-plated armor, shined so bright that the sun reflected off them."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_a235b695:
    # "There was no single battalion in all of Rosanna that was more well equipped. She knew Marion was somewhere among them."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_8574d6fe:
    # "Near the center, off to the back, the banner of house Rose waved. The gold and red banner, adorned with a black rose, stood defiant."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_5af3b1a6:
    # "Somewhere near that banner was Thomas."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_fda5fd81:
    # "The idea alone made Sarah's heart feel like stopping."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_c7853b0f:
    # "She had seen her brother shortly before he left for the battlefield. He had looked more like a child playing at being a soldier than a real soldier. Then again, perhaps that was what he was."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_52104b10:
    # "Underneath all the regalia and protocol, her brother was still a child, who had never seen a real battlefield in his life."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_83fca7ef:
    # "Sarah brought her hands together and offered up a soft prayer for the gods to hear."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b6d4fd98:
    # "Above all, even above victory, she prayed for Thomas to be safe."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_0d23bf8e:
    # "Suddenly, Sarah began to see stacks of smoke rise from Hassar's army."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_678a6854:
    # "The ranks in his army began to shift and move, confusion spread through them."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_2f3d3925:
    # "Sarah tried to make sense of it, but only after some time did she understand. The large trebuchets that had been built days before, were on fire."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_c22b74a2:
    # "Perhaps the gods did listen to her, she wondered."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_ae1d9255:
    # "She watched as Hassar's army tried to put out the flames, but most burned down entirely. Those saved, were in no working order."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_4ee351c0:
    # "The two armies faced off for nearly an hour, neither willing to move first."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_9a6fa06d:
    # "Hassar's army, now without any artillery, was trying to adapt their strategy."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_afa4e195:
    # "Suddenly, movements on the battlements drew Sarah's attention."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_cbe5f86a:
    # "Varga had issued the order to fire a first volley of arrows. In unison, all of the archers atop the wall drew back their bows and released a wave of arrows."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_4931b5ed:
    # "From so far away, the arrows seemed to fly slowly, but when they rained down on Hassar's army, Sarah could see the destruction they caused."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_24db480a:
    # "Soldiers collapsed, some from the arrows, others because the line began to break as soldiers tried to dodge the rain of arrows."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_fd7a19e6:
    # "Not soon had the first wave landed, when a second one quickly followed."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_e3aba765:
    # "The damage seemed only amplified. The chaos now spread further, deeper into Hassar's army, as discipline began to fracture."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_02422f1b:
    # "Sarah understood what Hassar did, they could not remain in their current position."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_bb77b83d:
    # "A loud battle horn rang out over the battlefield, and as if suddenly recovering all their training, Hassar's army began to move forward as one."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_0e3eb1e1:
    # "His army charged down the hill, the momentum causing the soldiers and their horses to move at an incredible speed."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b440361b:
    # "So massive was the charge, that Sarah saw a cloud of dust thrown up so large it blocked part of the battle."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_ca55879c:
    # "But she could still see the moment Hassar's vanguard clashed against Rosanna's frontline."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_794757c9:
    # "It was what Hassar had wanted to avoid, and exactly what Thomas had hoped for. Hassar's cavalry drove straight into a fortified front line, lined with pikes designed to counter the cavalry charge."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_73d45312:
    # "Sarah watched as countless soldiers and their horses had their momentum crushed to a halt, the row of pikes being raised up to stab upwards, knocking soldiers off their mounts, or stabbing the horses in the neck."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_ff7c9c5b:
    # "In mere moments, the entire charge had been brought to a halt, crushed on the iron frontline."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_00c13d96:
    # "Now, in front of the Rosannan army, the battlefield turned into a slaughter house."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_78e997e8:
    # "Unable to break their charge, the following waves of cavalry crashed atop the first wave, with one wave burrying the next."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_a341d775:
    # "Out ahead of the front line, the field turned into a nightmarish mix of body parts of horses and men, crawling through one another, crushing, drowning, breaking."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_993c517b:
    # "As another horn roared out, Rosanna's battle horn, the front line began to move forward."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_5c4db77f:
    # "Spears were switched for short blades, as the soldiers began to move forward, into the collapsing army of Hassar."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_6cc1e2e4:
    # "It was not so much a battle as it was a slaughter. Soldiers found the enemy trapped under their horses, and jabbed their blades into their necks, killing the enemy with ease."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_e3341fcb:
    # "They died without in great numbers and with little glory."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_794ea574:
    # "Rosanna's army swarmed forward, each soldier hungrily looking for an easy kill to boast about."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_257c9acb:
    # "Further in the back, Sarah saw Hassar's army beginning to regroup."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_78e512b4:
    # "The vanguard had been wiped out, but the later waves, having seen the strategic disaster, were able to abort their attack."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_532a612a:
    # "As they tried to regroup, Varga and his archers kept up the pressure, releasing wave after wave of arrows with deadly accuracy."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_93c368f1:
    # "Hassar's army split in two, each half rushing around the front line, hoping to circle around the pike wall."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_25b8967e:
    # "Hassar's cavalry was fast, and easily outran the infantry, but on the flanks they discovered Rosanna's heavy cavalry."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_6e24c883:
    # "Unable to outrun those, Hassar's troops found themselves quickly bogged down in a frenzied melee as the heavy cavalry closed the distance."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_60b78757:
    # "With the advantage of their speed lost, they now suffered the disadvantage of their light armor. Their weapons found no purchase against the plate armor of the heavy cavalry units."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_03a2049f:
    # "Trapped in a slog of a fight, Rosanna's infantry began to close in on Hassar's troops. On the outer edges, some horsemen were already beginning to be dragged down from their horses."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_99c41d4d:
    # "Sarah could only just make out men being thrown into the mud and stabbed to death."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b1ace961:
    # "Then, as if a lighting bolt shot through Hassar's army..."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_d165855d:
    # "It broke."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b308c047:
    # "On all sides, men began to ride off, wildly, in all directions."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_48bd5341:
    # "Even Sarah, with her little experience of war, could see that this was no strategy."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_16eeb042:
    # "Hassar's army was routing."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_bc4225ad:
    # "Trapped down hill, the speed of their escape was limited. Many men died from an arrow to the back."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_54a3abeb:
    # "Many others, too deep into the battle, only realized that their comrades had left them to die, when the Rosannan army encircled them."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_e1805410:
    # "Some fought on like lions, hoping to win some glory in their final moment, and yet others, seeing no purpose, simply dropped their weapons and waited for the end."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_e33d01cd:
    # "It was a massacre."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_503e8082:
    # "By the time the dust had cleared completely, Sarah could see that one regiment of the army had rushed up the hill and was now burning the entire tribal camp to the ground."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_6d9c3da4:
    # "All over, men were running away, only to find themselves ran down or caught by an arrow."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_ca1556ca:
    # "Off in the far distance, near the horizon, scattered war groups were seen still riding as fast as they could."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_fc26deba:
    # "As the sun began to set, the land turned an odd mix of gold and blood red."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b4637c02:
    # "Sarah had imagined both victory and defeat, but she still found herself surprised by how this moment made her feel."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b466bc3f:
    # "A rush of excitement ran through her body, a heat, eminating from her chest, drowned out all other sensations."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_0f50560d:
    # "Down below, a bloodbath, but in her heart, ecstasy."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_74f332a7:
    # "She had never dared to dream that delivering this carnage to her enemies, could feel so good."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b9865c45:
    # "As word of the victory spread through the capital, Sarah saw the citizens run out onto the street, celebrating and hailing the returning army as champions."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_1c26ada7:
    # "Loud, above all others, she heard them sing Thomas' name."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b5ebeb77:
    # "She could finally make out a man, dressed in full kingly regalia, leading the front of the returning army."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_965eef24:
    # "Thomas. He lived."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_7cb3757f:
    # "Less primal than the earlier emotion, but closer to her heart, she felt a deep joy, knowing that her brother had survived."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_6780a35a:
    # "Sarah left her room to go to the great hall and greet her brother."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b937ca4a:
    # "She arrived just as the men threw open the great doors of the castle and marched in, loudly screaming."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_dc808363:
    # t "My sister!"
    t ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_cf174827:
    # "Thomas' voiced boomed out over everyone else."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b82b98fd:
    # "He ran up towards Sarah and grabbed her, lifting her off her feet and spinning her around before putting her back down."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_e469ad99:
    # t "You should have seen me Sarah!"
    t ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_b7a0728f:
    # "Varga and Marion came up as well. All around them, soldiers were spilling into the castle."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_68fe877f:
    # m "The king, he fought as if posessed by the heroes of old."
    m ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_5b4737a8:
    # "Thomas, acting as if drunk, threw his arms around both Marion and Varga, pulling them closer."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_4a34d2e2:
    # t "Marion, Varga, you call me Thomas from now on. Enough with this king shit. We fought side by side, that makes you my equal in my book."
    t ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_de2b20d2:
    # "Varga laughed."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_1c2af5ad:
    # v "Very well, Thomas."
    v ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_db932e26:
    # "Marion joined in, but seemed pained by the lack of protocol."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_da090098:
    # m "Absolutely...Thomas."
    m ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_3e5ecd47:
    # "Others came up behind Thomas, vying for his attention. Thomas threw up his hands and made a face at Sarah, as if to suggest he was powerless, and let himself be dragged into the celebratory mob."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_55302656:
    # "Sarah saw an entirely new side of her brother."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_54d931ac:
    # "All around her, she saw soldiers dragging one another in every direction. She knew tonight the castle wouldn't sleep."
    ""

translate ru TheBattleForTheCapital_2c8ef95f:
    # "Sarah watched as people began to pull Varga and Marion away."
    ""

